gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Bulls 129, Timberwolves 123
gameRecap.excerpt: The Bulls completed a 23-point comeback and defeated the Timberwolves, 129-123. Coby White recorded 33 points (21 in the 4th quarter), seven 3PM, and seven assists for the Bulls, with DeMar DeRozan (33 points, five assists) and Nikola Vucevic (24 points, six rebounds) combining for 57 points in the victory. Anthony Edwards tallied 38 points, 12 rebounds, and five assists for the Timberwolves in the losing effort. The Bulls improve to 24-27, while the Timberwolves fall to 35-16.
